{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_05_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n今日は来てくれてありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは構わないが、俺を寮に呼び出して\n一体何をする気だ？",
      "startTime": 9.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "実はあれから、どうしたら食レポがうまくなるのか\nみんなに相談したんです",
      "startTime": 16.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら沙季ちゃんがそれを作ってくれました\nその分厚いレポート用紙の束を見て下さい！",
      "startTime": 22.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1766.6666683999993,
          "startTime": 19.8333333351
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "これを読み込んで極意を学んだ私は\nもはや食レポの達人と言っても過言じゃありません！",
      "startTime": 29.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "絶対過言だと思うが……\nそれで今日は勉強した成果を見せてくれる訳だな？",
      "startTime": 36.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今から、このレポートを見ながら\n用意しておいたドーナツを食レポします！",
      "startTime": 43.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと出来るかどうか、見ていて下さい！\nではさっそく、いただきまーす！",
      "startTime": 50,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、まずは見た目を褒める……見て下さい！\nこのドーナツ、真ん中に空いた穴が可愛いですね！",
      "startTime": 60.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "えーと、次は匂いを伝える……くんくん……なるほど！\nこのドーナツは無臭です！",
      "startTime": 74.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "次は熱いのか冷たいのか伝える……冷め切ってます！\n冷え切ったドーナツは美味しいのでしょうかー！？",
      "startTime": 85.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今のところ全然美味しそうに聞こえないな",
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まだ、ここからです！\n次は一口食べてコメントを言います！",
      "startTime": 95.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "はむっ……\nまずは食感を言う……えーと、フワフワです！",
      "startTime": 103.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "次に味は……すっごく甘いです！\nこれ一個で一日分の糖分を摂取した気分です！",
      "startTime": 117.5000000011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そして風味……こってりとした油の風味に、漂う\n高カロリー。これは罪悪感を覚える美味しさです！",
      "startTime": 129.4334333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　ちゃんと食レポ出来てましたか？",
      "startTime": 134.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "元気で明るいのはさくららしいが\n食レポのコメントとしてはダメなんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 141.0000100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……",
      "startTime": 143.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんから「コメントはこう言うといいですよ」\nって教わったので、その通り言ってみたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 150.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうりでさくららしくないコメントだと思ったよ\nこころは悪戯好きだから鵜呑みにしない方がいいぞ",
      "startTime": 159.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "……こ、こうなったら最後の手段です！",
      "startTime": 162.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "食レポのコメントを事前に考えておいて\n本番では丸暗記したコメントを言うんです！",
      "startTime": 169.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "これなら本番でも慌てずに\n料理にぴったりのコメントを言えますよね？",
      "startTime": 175.7333433334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "事前にコメントを用意しておくのか……\nまぁ、それなら確かに……",
      "startTime": 181.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、沙季ちゃんが例文を考えてくれてました\n今度はこれを丸暗記して言ってみますね",
      "startTime": 189.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.33333330001,
          "startTime": 192.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ～、これは美味しそうなチーズケーキですね～\nさっそく食べてみましょう～",
      "startTime": 203.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "はむっ……。チーズと卵のマリアージュが\nまろやかな風味となって口の中一杯に広がります",
      "startTime": 216.6333343334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "フワッと軽いのにしっとりなめらかな舌触りで\nクリーミーだけどコクがあって濃厚です",
      "startTime": 227.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "だけど全然しつこくないのでペロリと食べられます\nチーズの奥深い旨味を感じる素晴らしい一品ですね",
      "startTime": 236.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "……こんな感じでどうでしょうか",
      "startTime": 242.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "食レポのコメントとしては満点だが\n誰かに言わされている感が凄いな",
      "startTime": 248.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr026.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ちゃんとコメントしたのにダメって言われたら\n私はどうしたらいいんですか～",
      "startTime": 256.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 261.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、さくら\n今日は朝から元気がないじゃないか",
      "startTime": 264.400012207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "それが、昨日{user}さんが帰った後も\nずっと食レポの練習をしてたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 271.3333455403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか。食レポがうまく出来なくて）\n（落ち込んでいるんだな）",
      "startTime": 278.0666788737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
